Yes (well maybe a couple of candles!). 3 way fridges such as mine use a gas
flame to do the heating. I can vouch for its inefficiency! On 12 v it cant
keep an already cold fridge cold in summer. I think modern ones are more
efficient but that may just be better insulation.
